" reloads .vimrc -- making all changes active
map <silent> <Leader>sop :source ~/.vimrc<CR>:PlugInstall<CR>:bdelete<CR>:exe ":echo 'vimrc reloaded'"<CR>

" make backspaces deletejsensibly
